mdElement.text: Intended ML Use:1. There is a DOCUMENT for each department and employee. 2. The Department document DOES NOT have attributes representing its members or the hierarchy of that membership. Rather, that is kept in triples.3. The Employee document DOES NOT have attributes representing the employee's manager or department. Rather, that is kept in triples.
Notation:Main classes (orange): Department, EmployeeChild classes (yellow): Phone, Email, Address, GeoCoordinatesWhen a class has an attribute of another class type, the meaning here is COMPOSITION
